---
import LegalDoc from '~/components/LegalDoc.astro';
export const prerender = false;
---

<LegalDoc title="Shipping & Delivery Policy" activeNav="/shipping-policy">
  <p class="lead">DocFriends delivers <strong>digital written opinions only — no physical goods are
    shipped.</strong></p>

  <p>Once payment is received and you have submitted your case details, opinions are delivered
    electronically to your DocFriends dashboard, with an email notification, <strong>typically within
    [X] days</strong>. [Set the timeframe.] If you do not receive your opinion in the expected time,
    contact us (below).</p>

  <p class="note">(A delivery policy is required for Razorpay onboarding even for digital-only services;
    this page states that there is no physical shipment.)</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about delivery? See <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>.</p>
</LegalDoc>
